# jemdoc: menu{MENU}{research.html}, nofooter  
==Yanzhe (Murray) Lei \M 雷彦哲



=== Research Interests

- Applications: Pricing and Revenue Management,  Supply Chain Management and Logistics,  Retail Operations,  On-demand Platforms.


- Methodologies:  Stochastic Control,  Dynamic Optimization,  Online Learning and Optimization,  Asymptotic Analysis.




=== Publications


- [https://doi.org/10.1287/msom.2021.1012 Joint Product Framing (Display, Ranking, Pricing) and Order Fulfilment under the MNL Model for E-Commerce Retailers] (with Stefanus Jasin,  Joline Uichanco, and Andrew Vakhutinsky),  /Manufacturing \& Service Operations Management/,  2021. 


- [https://doi.org/10.1287/opre.2019.1906  Real-time Dynamic Pricing for Revenue Management with Reusable Resources, Advance Reservations, and Deterministic Service Time Requirements] (with Stefanus Jasin), /Operations Research/,  2020.  


- [https://pubsonline.informs.org/doi/abs/10.1287/msom.2017.0641 Joint Dynamic Pricing and Order Fulfillment for E-commerce Retailers] (with Stefanus Jasin and Amitabh Sinha), /Manufacturing \& Service Operations Management/,  2018.  
  -- [http://pomshk2017.ust.hk/studentpaper.html 2017 POMS-HK Student Paper Competition], Second Place. 



  
